If you want to use the sentinel1_reproject_to_unw.py within ./NW_drew/, you will need the relevant files (Whitcomb et al. ALT maps, Yi & Kimball et al.,
                                                                                                          ALT maps, and the Sentinel-1 incidence angle map).
To download these files, please follow to this link (insert link to data repository).

Otherwise, the warped files are provided for your convenience within ./NW_drew/.
